    "sha": "956f1c2",
    "message": "docs: Add LLM policy, PR template and update contribution guide\n\nLately, we encounter many contributions which are LLM-generated or\nassisted. Therefore, this commit aims to provide a policy regarding the\nuse of LLMs in `urunc`. Overall, the use of LLMs is allowed. However,\nwe want to make sure that the LLM users properly review and\nverify the generated output.\n\nDue to this change, we also need to update the contribution guide.\n\nFurthermore, we have created a PR template with a few questions that\nverify the contributors have read and followed the contribution guide.\n\nPR: https://github.com/urunc-dev/urunc/pull/404\nSigned-off-by: Charalampos Mainas \u003ccharalampos.mainas@gmail.com\u003e\nReviewed-by: Anastassios Nanos \u003cananos@nubificus.co.uk\u003e\nApproved-by: Anastassios Nanos \u003cananos@nubificus.co.uk\u003e",
